show.description: A young man rushes to the hospital with chest pain—only to find the doctor distracted on his phone. Angry, he threatens to call the police… until the doctor reveals he’s watching his home’s CCTV footage. What the footage shows leaves the young man gets shocked beyond belief—because the real story is just beginning.
